   Meetings

   The Fifth International Airborne Remote Sensing Conference has been
   rescheduled for 22-24 May 2002, in Miami, Florida, USA
   http://www.erim-int.com/CONF/5th_airborne/5thairmarkcalendar.html

   Cancelled!  Fifth Airborne Conference (San Francisco; September 17-20,
   2001)  This international conference will provide a unique forum for
   the exchange of ideas and information on the latest developments in
   airborne remote sensing systems and applications for addressing
   critical issues now facing the scientific, governmental, and commercial
   communities. The technical program will offer over 300 presentations by
   experts from around the world, and builds on the highly successful
   conferences held in Strasbourg, France; San Francisco; Copenhagen,
   Denmark; and Ottawa, Canada.

   Fourth International Airborne Remote Sensing Conference and Exhibition
   held in conjunction with the 21st Canadian Symposium on Remote Sensing,
   Ottawa, Canada, 21-24 June 1999
   http://www.erim-int.com/CONF/4th_airborne/4thair.html

   See discussion forum for further details



